query:
SELECT DISTINCT i.tenantId, t.name as tenant_name, COUNT(*) as posicoes
FROM inventory i
LEFT JOIN tenants t ON i.tenantId = t.id
LEFT JOIN products p ON i.productId = p.id
WHERE p.sku = '401460P'
GROUP BY i.tenantId, t.name;
